{"tid":1147874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"領展求上訴至終院被拒 被判無權限制電訊商在商場公用地方做工程","createTime":"2019-05-10T05:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T10:10:00.000Z","uid":3090,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"268717eda090d83a589ddef917318716ed392738","tid":1147874,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T05:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VhFWuAE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVhFWuAE.png&h=95357a78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n電訊盈科不滿進入領展旗下的屋邨商場進行設置和維修線路工程前，需事先向領展申請，以及每年支付1,800元牌照費，早前入稟控告領展，前年被判敗訴，其後上訴獲判得直。領展不服，早前申請上訴至終審法院，上訴庭今頒下判詞，認為領展沒有合理勝訴機會，故拒絕批出上訴許可，同時下令領展支付電盈逾14萬元訟費。不過，領展仍可直接向終院申請上訴。<br />\n<br />\n高院前年在裁決中指，作為商場業主的領展，有絕對的權利更改商場的公用範圍、並擁有有關地方的獨有佔用權。惟上訴庭不同意，認為領展非獨有佔用商場的公用地方，無權限制商戶所選取的電訊服務商進行工程。上訴庭認為，《電訊條例》的立法原意是希望市民可自由選擇公共電訊服務商，同時服務商亦可在公平和有效的情況下互相競爭；雖然租約訂明領展有權更改商場公用範圍，但領展無權剝奪商戶使用公用地方的權利，包括選擇公共電訊服務商。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：CACV275/17】<br />\n記者蔡少玲"},{"pid":"1ef2834817914922a672ed343a24eeea4fab0481","tid":1147874,"uid":188176,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:00:17.000Z","msg":"領展d人惡過狗"},{"pid":"4ec5e41b8f0c17985636938782f91d9758141a26","tid":1147874,"uid":52459,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:09:11.000Z","msg":"有錢人先可以對付到有錢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c9a32eaec06df4f4051f3982672920085a23e4","tid":1147874,"uid":236646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:36:49.000Z","msg":"領展真係大仆街"},{"pid":"e742111dfe2ba6f49adf0bd5f3aa25d3c2352f04","tid":1147874,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ec5e41b8f0c17985636938782f91d9758141a26","tid":1147874,"uid":52459,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:09:11.000Z","msg":"有錢人先可以對付到有錢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:39:01.000Z","msg":"領展仍可直接向終院申請上訴"},{"pid":"b1087e9f50d5df57d4a484d8af8de851829653f8","tid":1147874,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:40:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0503a2671c323ca95deb731a201d31e8a803fab8","tid":1147874,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:43:36.000Z","msg":"好波 領展仲走去買大陸商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14cdc887f0d457fc2c159c8940c64706e0745e24","tid":1147874,"uid":154669,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:10:24.000Z","msg":"以事論事，完全唔洗申請就可以隨意入人地私人範圍，咁都得？"},{"pid":"e75c0de87a1a395417d0843c872e972b960373aa","tid":1147874,"uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14cdc887f0d457fc2c159c8940c64706e0745e24","tid":1147874,"uid":154669,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:10:24.000Z","msg":"以事論事，完全唔洗申請就可以隨意入人地私人範圍，咁都得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:11:55.000Z","msg":"雖然租約訂明領展有權更改商場公用範圍，但領展無權剝奪商戶使用公用地方的權利，包括選擇公共電訊服務商。"},{"pid":"49075bdba640ff4d896ec85b18b8d7b5f0f1e6d3","tid":1147874,"uid":51388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14cdc887f0d457fc2c159c8940c64706e0745e24","tid":1147874,"uid":154669,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:10:24.000Z","msg":"以事論事，完全唔洗申請就可以隨意入人地私人範圍，咁都得？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:13:12.000Z","msg":"係無權阻止商戶使用電訊商及公用地方喎"},{"pid":"323ac69bb2ca74e342ab1dc22dbd85aee510d7d1","tid":1147874,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14cdc887f0d457fc2c159c8940c64706e0745e24","tid":1147874,"uid":154669,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:10:24.000Z","msg":"以事論事，完全唔洗申請就可以隨意入人地私人範圍，咁都得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:15:04.000Z","msg":"睇番公私定義"},{"pid":"6338860ef207612908916131c6b5d3c161689b8e","tid":1147874,"uid":154669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"49075bdba640ff4d896ec85b18b8d7b5f0f1e6d3","tid":1147874,"uid":51388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14cdc887f0d457fc2c159c8940c64706e0745e24","tid":1147874,"uid":154669,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:10:24.000Z","msg":"以事論事，完全唔洗申請就可以隨意入人地私人範圍，咁都得？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:13:12.000Z","msg":"係無權阻止商戶使用電訊商及公用地方喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:35:35.000Z","msg":"咁作為業主個商場範圍有啲咩事佢要孭飛，例如發生咩意外係咪可以當係公用範圍唔駛搵佢先？入商場搞工程前申請下先唔啱咩？"},{"pid":"aa92a47a512058f4ff31a4ad1354ed29ab41daff","tid":1147874,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:39:50.000Z","msg":"其實申請係要 但每年收費就可以拗"},{"pid":"68743386b1cc31655ced75a3ee53851bb6a057bb","tid":1147874,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ef2834817914922a672ed343a24eeea4fab0481","tid":1147874,"uid":188176,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:00:17.000Z","msg":"領展d人惡過狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:41:13.000Z","msg":"領展唔夠李家惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc64fb417a58f0b8abebb5dad0014f7d5a9c741","tid":1147874,"uid":48679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:43:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以事論事，完全唔洗申請就可以隨意入人地私人範圍，咁都得？</blockquote><br />\n係無權阻止商戶使用電訊商及公用地方喎</blockquote><br />\n咁作為業主個商場範圍有啲咩事佢要孭飛，例如發生咩意外係咪可以當係公用範圍唔駛搵佢先？入商場搞工程前申請下先唔啱咩？</blockquote><br />\nr&amp;r 你當係一個r?<br />\n領展係公用地方有responsibility ，但係無right 去阻止人用，<br />\n佢驚安全問題可以定立安全使用手則，而唔係咁樣收錢就入得，唔收就唔入得<br />\n<br />\n不過係領展蠢，想收番呢筆錢考立名目就得，學地鐵咁，入去做野要拎安全牌，考試要錢，上堂要錢，隨時賺得仲多過依家"},{"pid":"f92a3f5bceb675f25151cff0d0784322105d782e","tid":1147874,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ef2834817914922a672ed343a24eeea4fab0481","tid":1147874,"uid":188176,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:00:17.000Z","msg":"領展d人惡過狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T10:10:00.000Z","msg":"惡得過姓李嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}